    <description>
        <p>Program for controlling any HDMI LCD/OLED/Plasma/CRT, LED-Matrix or an LED-Cube with the proper backend.</p>
        <p>With the following features:</p>

        <ul>
            <li>Uploading files to the server</li>
            <li>Receiving status and errors from the server</li>
            <li>Changing and adjusting server-side settings</li>
            <li>Setting up and controlling interactive animations that are on the server</li>
            <li>Playing back MP4, JPEG and many other files on the server's LED-Matrix</li>
        </ul>
    </description>

